    "careerAndMoney": "Regarding career and finances, 4114 carries an important message about mirror number. Your angels are encouraging you to pay attention to your professional path and consider whether your current work aligns with your true purpose and values.\n\nIf you've been considering a career change, starting a new project, or taking your business in a different direction, 4114 is a sign that now may be the perfect time to make that move. The energy of this number supports new beginnings and the courage to pursue your authentic aspirations.",
