    "whenYouSee": "When you encounter angel number 7997, take a moment to pause and reflect. This is a sacred moment of communication between you and the spiritual realm. What were you thinking about? What situation were you facing? The context in which 7997 appears often contains important clues about the specific message your angels are trying to convey.\n\nSeeing 7997 is an invitation to heighten your awareness and pay closer attention to the signs, synchronicities, and guidance that surround you.",
    "numerologyBreakdown": "In the ancient science of numerology, 7997 carries its own unique vibrational signature. The meaning of 7997 is influenced by the individual digits that compose it, their positions, and the overall energy they create together.\n\nWhen reduced to its core, 7997 resonates with the energy of mirror number and reflection and self-awareness. Numerologists believe that repeated numbers like 7997 carry amplified spiritual significance because they appear through divine intervention rather than random chance.",
