    "whenYouSee": "When you encounter angel number 8866, take a moment to pause and reflect. This is a sacred moment of communication between you and the spiritual realm. What were you thinking about? What situation were you facing? The context in which 8866 appears often contains important clues about the specific message your angels are trying to convey.\n\nSeeing 8866 is an invitation to heighten your awareness and pay closer attention to the signs, synchronicities, and guidance that surround you.",
